entities.description: Categorical representation of variables in the survey.
The unweighted count of responses for each category in the survey.
The percentage representation of each category’s frequency in the survey data.
An entity representing the FBI Field Office for the respondents in the survey.
Possible responses or fields under FBI Field Office or similar categories.

relationships.description: Relates the survey to different categorical labels.
Indicates the unweighted frequency of each category.
Indicates the percentage representation of each category.
Connects a survey respondent to a specific FBI Field Office.
Links the data category to the FBI Field Office.
